    <p>
      Right now, it’s just an idea — an app integrating all the mindfulness practices and tools I use into one cohesive system around journaling experience. <a href="/ld" class="link">This system</a> includes a 10-year life vision, life calendar, annual goals, tasks, habits, key metrics, emotion tracking, and a daily journaling practice.
    </p>
